Class MemoryFileStoreWrite<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.operation.AbstractFileStoreWrite<T>
      • org.apache.paimon.operation.MemoryFileStoreWrite<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of record to write.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileStoreWrite<T>, Restorable<List<FileStoreWrite.State<T>>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AppendOnlyFileStoreWrite, KeyValueFileStoreWrite

    public abstract class MemoryFileStoreWrite<T>
extends AbstractFileStoreWrite<T>
    Base FileStoreWrite implementation which supports using shared memory and preempting memory from other writers.
